  "title": "Senior Sales Consultant (Maid Agency)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able Best has been trusted by Singapore families since 2003. We’re one of Singapore’s established maid agencies, known for professionalism, integrity, and results. As we expand, we’re seeking a proactive, self-driven Sales Consultant who can hit the ground running and take charge of their own performance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join a 20 year trusted brand with strong inbound leads and repeat customers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Enjoy autonomy and trust , we value results, not micromanagement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Competitive base salary + high commission per placement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Strong support team (admin, trainer, marketing) to handle backend work so you can focus on closing.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Clear growth path: Senior Consultant to Assistant Manager/Branch Manager potential.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Handle customer enquiries (calls, WhatsApp, walk-ins, online, social media, referrals etc) and build genuine relationships fast.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Understand customer needs and confidently recommend suitable helpers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Conduct interviews, manage expectations, and close placements independently.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Maintain active follow-ups and deliver an excellent customer experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Proactively explore new lead opportunities like referrals, partnerships, and creative marketing ideas.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Take ownership of your monthly targets and work towards consistent high performance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Who You Are</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Independent self-starter - you take initiative, stay motivated, and need minimal supervision.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Proven results - you know how to listen, handle objections, and close deals.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Goal-driven - you thrive under targets and love seeing your numbers grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>People person - confident communicator who builds trust naturally.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Strong in English; additional languages (Mandarin, Bahasa, Tagalog, Burmese) a plus.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Experience in maid agency sales, insurance, property, or service-based sales preferred.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>CEI certification is required for this role.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Basic Salary: $2,200 – $3,500 (depending on experience).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>High and tiered commissions package per successful placement, top performers earn well above base salary. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5.5 day work week (Alternate week off-days).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Autonomy, respect, and recognition for your results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Continuous training and advancement opportunities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Apply through this portal’s Apply button.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Only experienced candidates who can start fast and work independently will be shortlisted.</p>",
